{"tid":2150043,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，我發現咗個盲點大家一直無留意","createTime":"2020-08-10T18:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T08:05:37.000Z","uid":59522,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"216509d35dd712b356f79f2342131ae55bd87eff","tid":2150043,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"成日話香港人廢個班人好撚煩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2149940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2149940</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢個post一口氣講中曬我同人駁個陣啲point<br />\n然後個個都話：<br />\n咁唔通乜都唔做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有時<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">對話</span></span>有<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">盲點</span></strong></span><br />\n大家都要駁贏人，點解要駁？<br />\n<br />\n贏咗嘴炮都算係抗爭勝利咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜大家同路人叫得<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">手足</span></span></strong>唔係應該<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">討論</span></span>件事<br />\n幾時變咗鬥嘴鬥氣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足們係時候突破思想盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e00cd42725c557ad3406bfe5a8bf0e89d65757","tid":2150043,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:30:15.000Z","msg":"周庭被捕相關Twitter link<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sankei_news/status/1292816249143963649?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsankei_news%2Fstatus%2F1292816249143963649%3Fs%3D21&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=3f7006b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsankei_news%2Fstatus%2F1292816249143963649%3Fs%3D21&h=3eec057c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sankei_news/status/1292816249143963649?s=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mainichi/status/1292808382236131328?s=21\" data-sr-